FROM ubuntu:22.04@sha256:f9d633ff6640178c2d0525017174a688e2c1aef28f0a0130b26bd5554491f0da
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.source https://github.com/trstringer/manual-approval
COPY \
    ./external/price_server \
    /var/app/
WORKDIR /var/app
